two major military battles took place near the city : in 732 , the battle of poitiers ( also known as the battle of tours ) , in which the franks commanded by charles martel halted the expansion of the umayyad caliphate , and in 1356 , the battle of poitiers , a key victory for the english forces during the hundred years ' war .

frankly : this frankish king earned his byname " the hammer " by beating back the muslim invasion of france at poitiers in 732

